      <abstract id="aspace_e0eaee86107907579db69683dc902fdb">Louise Hall was a professor of Art and
        Architecture at Duke University from 1931-1975. The collection includes correspondence,
        memoranda, reports, printed material, clippings, color slides and papers related to the Art
        Department. The material ranges in date from 1934-1981.</abstract>
